description:
This session will be part of Workshop Wednesdays and is for everybody who is interested in attending regular online events, like study groups, workshops, "Intro to.." sessions.

We want to explore what people are interested in and plan for the next sessions.

Please let us know your interests, or just get chatting with organisers and members of CodeHub and Women's Tech Hub.
title: CodeHub @ Workshop Wednesdays - Forum session
